      <h3>Storing and Protecting Your Personal Information</h3>
      We may store Personal Information in locations outside our direct control (for instance, on servers or databases
      co-located with hosting providers).
      We use Security Sockets Layer (SSL) encryption technology to encrypt sensitive personal information (such as your
      payment information and geolocation) before it travels over the internet. Credit card numbers are never stored on
      our database or servers.
      <p>The security of your personal information is important to us. We follow generally accepted standards to protect
        the personal information submitted to us, both during transmission and once we receive it. However, no method of
        transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee
        its absolute security. If you have any questions about security on our Website, you can contact us at
        privacy@crowdfrica.org.</p>

      <h3>Making Changes To Or Removal of Account </h3>
      You may make any desired changes to your account information at any time by logging into your online account. If
      at any time a User wishes to review the information provided to Crowdfrica at the time of registering with
      Crowdfrica or at any time thereafter, you may do so by signing into your account and amending the same. Email us
      at privacy@crowdfrica.org for any support regarding your account.

      <h3>Refund</h3>
      <p>
        A donor has five (5) business days to request for a refund after contributing. If a campaign you support does
        not proceed to completion, we'll email you with the following options that would ensure that your donation still
        support a life-changing campaign. You can either:
        1) Choose another campaign that inspires you, or
        2) Donate into the general fund
        We send these emails the day after a campaign is rejected, canceled, interrupted, removed or suspended, and
        donors have 30 days to choose an option. If no action is taken in that time we'll apply the funds to an urgent
        campaign in need and we would still send you an update about the use of your donation. </p>

